source.name: Fire Permits
source.description: This data-set provides a list of all valid (current) permits issued by the Fire Department. The data-set includes the permit address, the type of permit, the permit holder, the conditions issued for approval (including maximum occupancy) and the expiration date if the permit is for a particular event.
